Class GamePlayingDownUnitTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.ucd.nearmiss.GamePlayingDownUnitTest

  • public class GamePlayingDownUnitTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Checks that the plane is going down the screen when the user is not touching the screen. Instrumentation test, which will execute on an Android device.
